{
  "stem": "21482.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Cracow, we wore a white armband with a blue Star of David.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Scared-- very scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very scared because we were marked, and there were so many things we were not allowed to do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not allowed to use the public transportation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not allowed to walk on a sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When-- when you saw a German soldier walk, you had to step off, get off the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was at that time, though, that we still-- of course we were not allowed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was at that time we still were able to have lessons, private lessons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And again, probably four of my girlfriends would have school in different houses every morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, it was in secret.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you had to be careful when you walked the street so nobody would see you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You couldn't carry any books.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You couldn't carry any paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You were not supposed to learn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we would meet in different homes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had professors that would come and teach us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because I was supposed to go into fifth grade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I-- I never did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When you were at these learning places, did you have to have guards then, too?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did you feel-- Yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were the parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mothers or somebody was always watching to make sure that the guards-- patrols were not coming.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was nobody-- if somebody would have spied on us, they would, you know, report us to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we were so young, and there was-- our parents wanted to make sure that we were learning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because at that time, they were still expecting the war not to last very long.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
